Class RegistryFactory

java.lang.Object
RegistryFactory
public class RegistryFactory extends Object
The RegistryFactory class is a factory for creating and holding registry needed for the camp management system. It provides static instances of Registry for specific types of objects (Enquiry, Student, CampCommittee, Staff, Admin, Suggestion, Camp).
